== Overview ==
The Avenger is a light [[:Category:Weapons (Cannons)|cannon]] which can cause significant damage for low level squads when used with [[:Category:Weapons (Shield Disruptors)|Shield Disruptors]].

== Where to Acquire ==
The Avenger can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
